From: uwu-gl <moegluwu0@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 18:31:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 26/43] PopUpWindowController: Refine Pop-Up View gesture
 handoff

Track the gesture launch path across WM, shell and transition payloads so Pop-Up View handoff stays consistent once the launch animation leaves SystemUI.

Change-Id: Ib62808d344b2132cf551a955891aa19ec9b677b0
